    <group id="eucs-04">
        <title>Organization of Information Security</title>
        <prop name="label" value="4." />
        <group id="eucs-04.ois-01">
            <title>OIS-01 Information Security Management System</title>
            <prop name="label" value="1." />
            <control id="eucs-04.ois-01.1" class="objective">
                <title>Objective</title>
                <prop name="label" value="1." />
                <part id="eucs-04.ois-01.1_stmt" name="statement">
                    <prop name="label" value="1." />
                    <p>The CSP operates an Information Security Management System (ISMS). The scope
                        of the ISMS covers the CSP's organisational units, locations and processes
                        for providing the cloud service.</p>
                </part>
                <part id="eucs-04.ois-01.2_stmt" name="statement">
                    <title>Requirements</title>
                    <prop name="label" value="2." />
                </part>
                <control id="eucs-04.ois-01.1b" class="requirements">
                    <title>OIS-01.1B</title>
                    <prop name="alt-identifier" value="OIS-01.1B" class="basic" />
                    <part id="eucs-04.ois-01.1b_stmt" name="statement">
                        <p>The CSP shall document the scope of the cloud service that is under the
                            CSPâ€™s control and the boundaries.</p>
                    </part>
                </control>
                <control id="eucs-04.ois-01.2b" class="requirements">
                    <title>OIS-01.2B</title>
                    <prop name="alt-identifier" value="OIS-01.2B" class="basic" />
                    <part id="eucs-04.ois-01.2b_stmt" name="statement">
                        <p>The CSP shall have an information security management system (ISMS),
                            covering at least the operational units, locations, people and processes
                            for providing the cloud service.</p>
                    </part>
                </control>
                <control id="eucs-04.ois-01.3b" class="requirements">
                    <title>OIS-01.3B</title>
                    <prop name="alt-identifier" value="OIS-01.3B" class="basic" />
                    <part id="eucs-04.ois-01.3b_stmt" name="statement">
                        <p>The CSP shall provide documented information about the ISMS as applied to
                            the cloud service, covering what is applicable to the cloud service
                            regarding:</p>
                        <p>Scope and boundaries of the ISMS;</p>
                        <p>The context of the CSP;</p>
                        <p>Description of how the cloud service is covered by activities in the
                            ISMS; and</p>
                        <p>How the security of the cloud service is maintained and improved</p>
                    </part>
                </control>
            </control>
